{"tid":207436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電競列亞運項目 苦練《英雄聯盟》2022贏金牌","createTime":"2017-04-19T01:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T05:23:44.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"994ca22eaeefafc96d18942863a2ba855de27f1e","tid":207436,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"亞奧理事會（OCA）與阿里體育周一在杭州舉行記者會，宣布成為戰略合作夥伴，雙方將共同持續、大力推進電競運動，2022年杭州亞運會並會首次成為正式比賽項目。<br />\n電競近年發展迅速，社會對於電競行業亦愈見重視。據OCA方面表示，電競在亞洲以至全世界受到數以百萬計青少年歡迎，今年9月在土庫曼舉行的第五屆亞洲室內暨武術運動會（AIMAG），電競已成為了示範項目，明年在印尼舉行的第18屆亞運會將再次把電競列為示範項目，到2022年杭州第19屆亞運會，電競則會首次成為正式比賽項目；目前電競主要遊戲為《英雄聯盟》League of Legend及FIFA，這兩款遊戲在中、台、韓非常受歡迎，並有職業選手參賽。  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170418/56579478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170418%2F56579478&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=6bca42a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170418%2F56579478&h=c015bfd1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170418/56579478</a>"},{"pid":"e8e324ee460c6f605cdae008ce3a3c5569f393f5","tid":207436,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"電競係咪蝗語？我叫開打機"},{"pid":"bb950fc51cbab5bc81de57c0a37ab7f7af818a87","tid":207436,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"lol 到2020 仲未執先算啦"},{"pid":"3b13845ed00e55665d9702e29eed39fa45b721e2","tid":207436,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電競係咪蝗語？我叫開打機</blockquote><br />\n都唔同意思，電子競技 同 純粹玩遊戲唔同"},{"pid":"9cffe386e2d2087505793ec549f4d3c5a8c37e39","tid":207436,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T01:35:35.000Z","msg":"鬥打機成為亞運會項目<br />\n笑死朕<br />\n<br />\n咁有咩禁藥唔準食"},{"pid":"892caadaf6ab9